<br>
SLOW is SLOW: the mob attackes less frequently.<br>
SNARE is SNARE:  the mob's rate of movement is decreased.<br>
DOT is DOT:  the mob is suffering from reduction of hitpoints over time<br>
MEZ is MEZ:  the mob is unable to move or attack<br>
<br>
